## Notes on Third-Party Content

This repository may include reference images and PDF templates that describe
layouts of Primark-branded retail labels. These assets are included solely as
**format references** for factories supplying Primark — they are **not**
official Primark artwork and **do not** grant any right to use Primark's
trademarks, logos, or brand identity. Users are responsible for ensuring
their own use of such layouts complies with their contractual obligations to
Primark or any other brand owner.

The MIT license above applies to the skill definitions, code snippets, and
documentation authored by the contributors; it does not grant rights over any
third-party trademarks referenced within the materials.
